I'm Diego. A second-year master's student in the MA in Social Sciences at the Carlos III - Juan March Institute in Madrid, and a political scientist in the making.

I am particularly interested in different topics in historical political economy, ranging from the politics of early educational reforms, political behavior after suffrage expansions, or the political consequences of land reforms.

